    "7306113": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the people who are blocking the cave",
        "Step": "You arrived at the cave containing the Zohrah Mushroom. However, the entrance to the cave seems to be blocked by some familiar — but unpleasant — people...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "Stop."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ziri",
                    "T": "You can't enter."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why are you people here again? Come on! What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Out on a date, perchance?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Guarding something important, perhaps?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph, you can't even come up with an answer, that's so suspicious!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "You can't enter."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ziri",
                    "T": "You can't enter, and that's that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Are you two serious?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You two think you can stop me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "...It's three. Three at least."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Pardon my boys, they're not good with words. I've already made it clear that I'd never threaten friends. It was just a warning, that's all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Whatever you want is not in this cave, unless it's death. Everything dies in there, no matter what it is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Don't try to scare us. We've experienced all kinds of danger!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Why would I try to scare you when I'm elated to see you again? I'm just worried about your safety."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "We discovered a Withering Zone inside. That's why we've drawn a circle at the entrance to warn commoners from wandering in."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Where's the circle then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Where's the circle?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Tell me now, where's the circle!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "I, uh, he, uh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ziri",
                    "T": "You're the boss, so there's one if you say so."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Ahem. Regardless, my friends, the cave is treacherous and unpredictable. I suggest you leave right now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How come it's you again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "\"Again\"? Well, I guess fate works in mysterious ways. It's got plans for us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm no commoner."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "That's what we all thought when we picked up our first sword! Until we saw blood for the first time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Alright, alright... Don't listen to me, then. Like I said, I warned you out of the goodness of my heart. Go in if you insist... It's not like you're hiring us to be your bodyguards, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Come on, boys. We're out of here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Ahem, let's go!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7306114": {
        "Desc": "Go into the cave where the Zohrah Mushroom is located",
        "Step": "After having a not-so-pleasant talk with Lunja and her gang, you finally resume your search for the Zohrah Mushroom. The target you're after should be in the cave.",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7306130": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Aranakin",
        "Step": "Aranakin seems to have something to say to you...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "#I'm here! Nara {NICKNAME}, and White Floaty!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa, where have you been?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Some bad \"sand grains\" were here. They were up to no good, so I didn't want to come out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are you referring to those Eremite mercenaries? Are you afraid of them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "White Floaty wrong! I'm not afraid! They're weak, I'm strong!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Strong to the point of hiding?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "#No, no! Hmph! Nara {NICKNAME} only says irritating things!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We have to be careful from now on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME} is right. Be careful of those bad \"sand grains\" and their wicked thoughts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Anyway, the water here... It's showing some strange colors. Do you think it's because of..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Withering."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Marana."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Correct, it is Marana. It permeates the water and dances like mist... So you can't drink the water, and it makes the plants sick."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Thanks to Zohrah Mushroom, Marana has withdrawn a little. But Marana is still too much around. Zohrah Mushroom is not feeling well. He's in danger."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But the place is all affected by The Withering. How are we supposed to get close?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Hmm... Look at that odd old rock over there! Repair it and the crack in the pond should open big enough... to drain the water away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But... even if we can drain the water, what are we going to do with The Withering here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Well... We'll worry about that later! We also have to break the seal protecting Zohrah Mushroom to let him join us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay, got it. Let's get to work then!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
