    "7306140": {
        "Desc": "Use Kusava to break the seal on the Zohrah Mushroom",
        "Step": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Minum, Ziri, I got it! Find a messenger to inform the client! And we're leaving now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Those were tough opponents. The Withering couldn't stop them, Anqa and Isan got hurt too. So before they catch up with us..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Minum",
                    "T": "Boss..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Didn't you hear what I said? What are you waiting for?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ziri",
                    "T": "#{M#He}{F#She} is here already."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm all ears. Please continue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is this how you treat your \"friends\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "*sigh* I just can't get rid of you, can I..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Sorry, my \"friends,\" we just wanted the Zohrah Mushroom for our client. Just business, nothing personal."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Friends? We're not friends! How can you still call us that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "What do you mean, little one? I already apologized. Let's just let bygones be bygones, okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aaahh!! You...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Seriously, you've proven you're extraordinary by giving Anqa and Isan a good thrashing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "I admire warriors like you. It's my honor to be your friend. But... business is business. I'm sure you understand, right? I hate to break our friendship."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "It would be such a shame to let some boring business get in between us friends!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just get to the point."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Hand over the Zohrah Mushroom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Take it easy, my friend. You're the ones who are cornered in this cave. You wanna risk your life for it? Not a problem."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "But I'd rather not see more of my people get hurt over a lousy mushroom. The pay's just not worth it. So, let's make a deal..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Who would trust a scammer like you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lunja",
                    "T": "Well, that depends on how much you're willing to pay."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
