    "7306107": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "These guys are weird, so eager to get chummy..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'd better be careful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Yes, yes, you should be careful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, since you both say so..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Hey! You startled me!!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's Paimon's line!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hm... Speaking of which, little one, who are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Aranakin isn't a \"little one,\" Aranakin is Aranakin!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "You can't listen to those sand grains. They're liars with bad minds who are here for the Aranara!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Bad minds...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Bad minds, bad bad minds!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are the \"sand grains\" you are talking about?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Sand is Valuka, and those sand grains are a group of bad Nara Valuka. I don't like sand, it's coarse, rough, and irritating. And it gets everywhere..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What...? Paimon didn't get that at all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "White Floaty is silly, so White Floaty didn't get it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wha— Hey!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He's talking about those people from just now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "They must have some sort of a scheme."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME} smart, that's what Aranakin means."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? You know our names?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "#Yes, Aranakin smart. When you talked to them, I listened. I heard that the Nara's name is \"{NICKNAME}\" and that your name is \"Paimon.\" But Floaty Paimon is silly and doesn't understand Aranakin."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Floaty Paimon is like that, it's true."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! Paimon's not silly!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Aragaru sent us here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "I know. All the grass and trees, one by one, were passing the message, and it got to me. So I knew I would see you here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Mawtiyima is feeling sick, Marana is getting bigger. We must go quickly. Quickly!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "W—Wait a second, we don't even know where we're going!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "Zohrah Mushroom! We need Zohrah Mushroom, to prepare Arahaoma. We need Arahaoma, to help Mawtiyima be lively again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakin",
                    "T": "I know where Zohrah Mushroom is, I take you there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright... Hey, wait for us!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
