    "7306616": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Aranaga",
        "Step": "Aranaga seems to have something to say to you...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Yajna Grass is right here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Excuse me, please. Let me say a few words, with the Yajna Grass."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Though it's the garden of Aranaga, there is only one Yajna Grass here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "There were many, once. Whenever the moon rose or fell, a Yajna Grass would grow..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "But it came, Marana. In the wake of Marana, walking Shroom-Kin came. They ate and ate. Died, many Yajna Grass, leaving just this one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then what are you guys gonna do after we use the Yammering Grass to make Arahaoma?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "It's the Yajna Grass, White Mushroom silly. But no need to worry. The important seeds are kept safe by Jamikayomars. The gate of Mawtiyima, Jamikayomars is guarding."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon sees..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Doesn't Aranaga still need to catch up on the old times, with the Yajna Grass...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There's no time to lose. Let's take the Yajna Grass away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Aranaga whispers to the plant for a while..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Willing to become Arahaoma, he said."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "And... Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Next, let's go to Jamikayomars, together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then lead the way, little bean!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Little bean, not! Aranaga! Floaty is mean!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay, okay, Paimon is not mean!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7306617": {
        "Desc": "Return to Aranaga's little garden",
        "Step": "Aranaga's little garden is close to Jamikayomars. You can't miss it.",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7306618": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Aranaga",
        "Step": "Aranaga seems to have something to say to you...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Over here, Jamikayomars is!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Nara Varuna's memory cup grows here, so the name is Jamikayomars. Jamikayomars is guarding Mawtiyima, so cannot enter, those bad guys."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But... Where, the Marana you spoke of is?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yes, anything unusual, we haven't seen..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Talking like this? Since when did you start..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Talking in this way as well, Paimon is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! That's none of your business!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Mawtiyima has been infiltrated by Marana. So we must infuse Arahaoma into Jamikayomars."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "He will open the path for us, once Jamikayomars remembers it all, then we go in and rescue Mawtiyima."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is it, Arahaoma?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "The essence of memory, messenger that drives away death, the elixir Arahaoma is. Carries our memories, carries our life, the elixir Arahaoma."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "To make Arahaoma, three types of plants are required: Yajna Grass and its friends, Barsam Flower and Zohrah Mushroom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Under the moonlight, with the precious memories, refine them, so that the potion can be complete."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "After Arahaoma is offered, Jamikayomars will awaken, then our memory will flow out, flow into the forest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Mawtiyima, will be saved."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the memory..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Nara language, I don't know how to use. Memory, dead, frozen, many Nara believe. Memory will be lost, many Nara believe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "But it is alive, flowing, not lost... It needs to be nourished."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "There are dreams because there is memory. Memory is nourished, so there is life."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "So, it can grow, the thing to repel Marana."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Oh, what's that Nara word... I'm stuck. Don't know how to say it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You mean courage?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Yes, that's right. Seeds must be sturdy to withstand Marana. Only seeds with hard shells will not let Marana penetrate their soft cores. Only seeds with thorns will prick Marana."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm guessing you mean \"hope\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "#Yeah, right you are, Golden Nara {NICKNAME}. The thing that flows, cannot be seen, cannot be touched... Hope. Like the wind... But it never dissipates, like a dream."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is it... wisdom?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Wisdom... Flowing memory, wisdom. Stagnant wisdom, Marana's lair. So, living memory gives birth to living wisdom, and dead Marana will dissipate. Nara Varuna said... that the dead cannot defeat the living."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "But first, we must have Arahaoma to awake Jamikayomars. And to make Arahaoma, we need the Barsam Flower and the Zohrah Mushroom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "They have already been gathered."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME}, exactly the same as Nara Varuna... And golden too. Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranaga",
                    "T": "Please come back when the moon rises over the tallest tree. The ritual to obtain Arahaoma will begin then."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
